  "title": "🎉 Events & Sales Branding Associate (Entry Level)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>EMINENCE ORGANIZATION is a dynamic events and sales company that thrives on creativity and energy. Our young and vibrant team brings fresh ideas to the table, ensuring every project is as bold and exciting as the next. Here, we don’t just market products or drive sales—we create moments that stick. Let’s make magic happen!</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join a fun, energetic team to work on roadshows and pop-up events, represent exciting brands, and develop strong communication and sales skills. No experience needed — full training provided.✨</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver brand presentations and product information clearly to event attendees to increase brand awareness and customer interest</li><li>Initiate and maintain positive interactions with customers to create memorable event experiences and encourage engagement</li><li>Assist in setting up and dismantling event booths and materials to ensure smooth event operations</li><li>Collaborate effectively with team members to support event execution and achieve shared goals</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Outgoing, positive attitude with a team-oriented mindset</li><li>Enjoys engaging with diverse groups of people</li></ul>",
